        <updateDate>2010-02-16T19:12:34Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Dollars to the Classroom Act - Requires at least 95% of any federal funds made available to a state by the Secretary of Education for elementary or secondary education to be used for: (1) academic purposes; and (2) classroom-related purposes or at the school level.</p>]]></text>
